《'''脫歐小電影'''》（{{lang-en|''Brexit: The Movie''}}）是2016年英國的[[紀錄片|紀錄片]]，由{{tsl|en|Martin Durkin (television director)|馬田·鄧堅}}編劇和監製，提倡[[英國脫歐|英國脫離欧洲联盟]]。本片透過[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]眾籌而製作，2016年5月11日在倫敦首映、翌日在[[YouTube|YouTube]]和[[Vimeo|Vimeo]]發佈。

== 製作 ==
本片由{{tsl|en|Martin Durkin (television director)|馬田·鄧堅}}編劇和監製，提倡選民在2016年6月的英國[[英國去留歐盟公投|英國去留歐盟公投]]中，支持英國脫離[[欧洲联盟|欧洲联盟]]（簡稱[[英國脫歐|英國脫歐]]）<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.vice.com/en_uk/article/vd8xpm/brexit-the-movie-review-sam-kriss-martin-durkin|title='Brexit: the Movie' Reveals Why the Upper Classes Are So Excited About the Prospect of Leaving the EU|work=Vice|date=2016-05-12|last=Kriss|first=Sam|accessdate=2020-09-13|archive-date=2020-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200105141333/https://www.vice.com/en_uk/article/vd8xpm/brexit-the-movie-review-sam-kriss-martin-durkin|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Exp>{{cite news|url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/politics/668346/brexit-movie-feature-length-documentary-film-EU-Europe-Britain-exit|title=New feature-length documentary film shows why we must vote for Brexit|work=The Daily Express|date=2016-05-09|last=Russell|first=Andy|accessdate=2020-09-13|archive-date=2016-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523104950/https://www.express.co.uk/news/politics/668346/brexit-movie-feature-length-documentary-film-EU-Europe-Britain-exit|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本片亦是透過[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]][[群眾募資|眾籌]]而製作，目標是在2016年2月26日前有1,500人捐獻共£100,000<ref name="CityAM">{{cite web|url=http://www.cityam.com/235494/eu-referendum-filmmaker-martin-durkin-says-brexit-the-movie-crowdfunding-campaign-has-hit-its-100000-target-ahead-of-its-may-release-date|title=EU referendum: Filmmaker Martin Durkin says "Brexit: The Movie" crowdfunding campaign has hit its £100,000 target|last=Haslett|first=Emma|date=2016-02-26|website=City A.M.|publisher=City A.M. Limited|access-date=2016-06-24|archive-date=2018-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106235657/http://www.cityam.com/235494/eu-referendum-filmmaker-martin-durkin-says-brexit-the-movie-crowdfunding-campaign-has-hit-its-100000-target-ahead-of-its-may-release-date|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Express/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/brexitthemovie/brexit-the-movie|title=Brexit The Movie|publisher=Kickstarter|accessdate=2017-04-17|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108164336/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/brexitthemovie/brexit-the-movie|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最終有超過1,800人參與，籌集到超過£300,000<ref name=About/>。

== 發佈 ==
2016年5月11日，電影在{{tsl|en|Leave.EU}}的籌辦下<ref name=Exp/>，於[[伦敦|伦敦]][[萊斯特廣場奧迪安電影院|萊斯特廣場奧迪安電影院]]首映<ref name="HuffPo">{{Cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/owen-bennett/brexit-the-movie-_b_9915388.html|title='Brexit – The Movie' Paints a Thatcherite Dream Of Post-EU Britain|last=Bennett|first=Owen|date=2016-05-12|work=[[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]]|access-date=2016-06-24|via=|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314191604/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/owen-bennett/brexit-the-movie-_b_9915388.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。翌日在[[YouTube|YouTube]]和[[Vimeo|Vimeo]]兩個[[流媒体|流媒体]]平台發佈<ref name=":1">{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160623232110/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UTMxfAkxfQ0|archivedate=2016-06-23|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UTMxfAkxfQ0|title=Brexit: The Movie}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite AV media|url=https://vimeo.com/166378572|title=Brexit: The Movie|date=2016-05-12|type=Film|language=en|accessdate=2016-06-24|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108115717/https://vimeo.com/166378572|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中在YouTube，電影分為二十六個部分上載<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160718050511/https://www.brexitthemovie.com/|archivedate=2016-07-18|url=https://www.brexitthemovie.com/|title=Home|website=Brexit: The Movie|publisher=Wag TV|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 迴響 ==
截至脫歐公投當日（即2016年6月23日），本片在YouTube的觀看人次超過150萬<ref name=":1" />，[[電影評論|評價]]有正有負。

保羅·寶雲在親脫歐的《[[每日快報|每日快報]]》撰文，讚揚電影大大揭露歐盟內部缺乏問責制度的問題<ref name="Express">{{cite news|url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/politics/669367/Brexit-The-Movie-reveals-terrifying-TRUTH-about-anti-democratic-EU|title=Watch: Brexit movie reveals how smug Eurocrats have shot our democracy down in flames|last=Baldwin|first=Paul|date=2016-05-12|work=[[每日快報|The Daily Express]]|access-date=2016-06-24|via=|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108133728/https://www.express.co.uk/news/politics/669367/Brexit-The-Movie-reveals-terrifying-TRUTH-about-anti-democratic-EU|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Public Relations and Communications Association|公關及溝通協會}}的尼古拉斯·鄧麥卡菲形容電影「易消化」和「風趣」，但覺得電影發佈得有點遲<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.prweek.com/article/1394642/brexit-movie-shows-power-simplifying-story|title=Brexit: The Movie shows the power of simplifying the story|last=Dunn-McAfee|first=Nicholas|work=PRWeek|date=2016-05-12|accessdate=2020-09-13|archive-date=2018-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180325052552/https://www.prweek.com/article/1394642/brexit-movie-shows-power-simplifying-story|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]》褒貶皆有，先是贊同電影具有說服力，但也有可能令選民改投留歐派，並抨擊電影過於依賴[[族群刻板印象|種族偏見]]並忽視某些角度<ref name="HuffPo" />。

《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》提及電影嘗試打入[[英國保守主義|保守派]]和[[反建制|反建制]]的市場，形容是「[[艾茵·兰德|蘭德]]派的[[英國自由意志主義|自由主義]]夢遺」，但批評電影有內容不一致的情況<ref>{{Cite magazine|last=Lowe|first=Josh|date=2016-05-12|title=Brexit: The Movie is a Libertarian's Wet Dream|url=http://www.newsweek.com/brexit-movie-review-nigel-farage-michael-gove-douglas-carswell-eu-referendum-459234|magazine=[[新闻周刊|Newsweek]]|doi=|pmid=|access-date=2016-06-24|archive-date=2020-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215013825/https://www.newsweek.com/brexit-movie-review-nigel-farage-michael-gove-douglas-carswell-eu-referendum-459234|dead-url=no}}</ref>。德國報章《[[法兰克福汇报|法兰克福汇报]]》斥責電影毫無提及親歐派觀點，觀點過於單一<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.faz.net/aktuell/wirtschaft/wirtschaftspolitik/film-brexit-the-movie-soll-waehler-fuer-eu-austritt-gewinnen-14228486.html|title=Brexit - der Film|work=[[法兰克福汇报|Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung]]|date=2016-05-12|last=Theurer|first=Marcus|language=de|author=|publisher=|accessdate=|format=|archive-date=2018-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180325052452/http://www.faz.net/aktuell/wirtschaft/wirtschaftspolitik/film-brexit-the-movie-soll-waehler-fuer-eu-austritt-gewinnen-14228486.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

